></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/wiki/Socialist_Alternative_(United_States)\" title=\"Socialist Alternative (United States)\">Socialist Alternative</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/wiki/Socialist_Equality_Party_(United_States)\" title=\"Socialist Equality Party (United States)\">Socialist Equality Party</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/wiki/Socialist_Organizer\" title=\"Socialist Organizer\">Socialist Organizer</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/wiki/Socialist_Party_USA\" title=\"Socialist Party USA\">Socialist Party</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/wiki/Socialist_Workers_Party_(United_States)\" title=\"Socialist Workers Party (United States)\">Socialist Workers Party</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/wiki/Spartacist_League_(US)\" title=\"Spartacist League (US)\">Spartacist League</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/wiki/Students_for_a_Democratic_Society_(2006_organization)\" title=\"Students for a Democratic Society (2006 organization)\">Students for a Democratic Society (2006 organization)</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/wiki/Workers_World_Party\" title=\"Workers World Party\">Workers World Party</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/wiki/World_Socialist_Party_of_the_United_States\" title=\"World Socialist Party of the United States\">World Socialist Party</a></div></div></td></li></ul>\n</tr><tr><td style=\"padding:0 0.1em 0.4em\">\n<div class=\"NavFrame collapsed\" style=\"border:none;padding:0\"><div class=\"NavHead\" style=\"font-size:105%;background:transparent;text-align:left;border-top:none;text-align:center;font-weight:normal;\"><i>Former</i></div><div class=\"NavContent hlist\" style=\"font-size:105%;padding:0.2em 0 0.4em;text-align:center\">\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/wiki/Social_Democracy_of_America\" title=\"Social Democracy of America\">Social Democracy of America</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/wiki/Socialist_Labor_Party_of_America\" title=\"Socialist Labor Party of America\">Socialist Labor Party of America</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/wiki/Social_Democratic_Party_of_America\" title=\"Social Democratic Party of America\">Social Democrati